also be viewed by switching on to http://www.laknews.lk from 8
p.m. onwards on January 25 after polling ends.
</P>
<P>
The reports said the move, for the benefit of Sri Lankans
living abroad, is sponsored by Lakvision, the pioneer worldwide
news service website.
</P>
<P>
Analysts here said the bitterly contested NWPC election in a
single province has drawn the attention of the whole country,
because the results are expected to signal winners of future polls
in other five provinces. 
