<HEADLINE> Major News Items in Leading Pakistani Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, January 24 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news
items in leading Pakistani English newspapers on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The News:
</P>
<P>
-- The federal cabinet unanimously decided Saturday to extend
